OL,5, Thousands of tonnes of oil have spilled
OL,6, routinely into UK waters from oil and  
OL,7, gas production threatening marine life 
OL,8, like porpoises and orcas, according to 
OL,9, data shown exclusively to BBC News.    
OL,11,FThe spills took place over five years  
OL,12,Fand some of them hit areas meant to    
OL,13,Fprotect wildlife, the data shows.      
OL,15,FCompanies are allowed to spill some oil
OL,16,Fin day-to-day production, but 40% of   
OL,17,Fmonitored releases breached permits.   
OL,19,FAn industry representative said it     
OL,20,Ftakes all releases very seriously.     
